{"tid":402596,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳帆稱一地兩檢最有效率 冀勿忘初衷","createTime":"2017-09-16T14:18:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-17T02:29:51.000Z","uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"67fcb687b2d9767ef3a86ad1d871f3e51bffa119","tid":402596,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T14:18:14.000Z","msg":"運輸及房屋局局長陳帆表示，一地兩檢是決定興建高鐵時，已經希望推行，認為應「勿忘初衷」。<br />\n<br />\n陳帆在一個活動與青年交流時，有中學生提出，一地兩檢受到相當爭議，包括被質疑「割地」。陳帆重申，兩地兩檢並非做不到，一地兩檢是最初興建時的目標，相關技術問題亦已解決，重申一地兩檢是最有效率的做法。<br />\n<br />\n亦有年青人提到樓價高的問題，陳帆表示，他自己亦無置業，年青人可以考慮是否一定置業，是否可以將資源用於其他地方，例如去聽音樂會甚至去日本旅遊，認為都是一種選擇，認為生命是多角度，目標不需要單一。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/陳帆稱-地兩檢最有效率-冀勿忘初衷-042348856.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E9%99%B3%E5%B8%86%E7%A8%B1-%E5%9C%B0%E5%85%A9%E6%AA%A2%E6%9C%80%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88%E7%8E%87-%E5%86%80%E5%8B%BF%E5%BF%98%E5%88%9D%E8%A1%B7-042348856.html&d=ABDvUAqr3kFZA1634wcthAtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=d7a12485\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/陳帆稱-地兩檢最有效率-冀勿忘初衷-042348856.html</a>"},{"pid":"95fcbfb2a6e3d4666b01a0365babd53afdcadccf","tid":402596,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T14:51:57.000Z","msg":"當年鄭汝華唔係咁講喎"},{"pid":"fc47519bacba2424e411e3937c3118e50cf787d8","tid":402596,"uid":71583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T22:01:48.000Z","msg":"我初衷係反高鐵"},{"pid":"9aeaf5afba28e8d7faae0c05ff6c9a281d87e9a4","tid":402596,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T02:27:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當年鄭汝華唔係咁講喎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一朝天子一朝臣<br />\n9up完就會走人"},{"pid":"f036ebd231a04371e3cf130caaaf0cb793c3ccc8","tid":402596,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T02:28:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我初衷係反高鐵</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"286a04811f22c1724e32a300e5b